  <p class="gd-lede">Alaska is the sport's trophy. Iceland is its most accessible world-class week. Both are extraordinary, and they suit different skiers. Here is the honest comparison across terrain, difficulty, cost and weather — then see <a href="/packages">the Iceland packages</a> or the wider view on <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
